hEoTZ3FfEXA.title: GS - Walkthrough - Episode - 97 - Into the Venus Lighthouse
hEoTZ3FfEXA.description:
-Status-
From where we enter the Babi Lighthouse to where we find our way into the Tunnel Ruins.

This is a short video on how to get past the the gate to the Tunnel entrance. Expect the next video to be a full scale walkthrough of both of the alternate entrances to the Venus Lighthouse.

Enter the Lighthouse and talk to the people lying there. Enter the Inner Lighthouse and head northeast to the door on the right. Once your done with that, head to the door on the left parellel to the door you just came out of. Then into the next door and down the slope.

Once you get down to the basement you will see Faran with a bunch of other people lookig for Sheba, the mysterious Jupiter Adept.

If you walk close enough to them you will trigger a cutscene and will show all the men there that you have the power to open the door.

After the long conversation you will be forced to go alone into the Venus Lighthouse but before that you will be forced to go through the Tunnel Ruins.

This concludes this episode. The rest will continue on episode 98.

Rate, Comment, and Subscribe if you find any of these videos helpful.
